  "title": "Assistant Store Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>About Company:</strong></p><p>Our client is a leading sneaker and sport fashion retailer. They offer a wide selection of footwear, apparel, and accessories from top brands.</p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><p>- Maintain customer retention by providing first-class service</p><p>- Deal with inquiries and complaints and resolve the issue/request</p><p>- Drive consistency within your internal teams to achieve the highest service levels</p><p>- Ensure that targets are achieved and, where possible, exceeded</p><p>- Analyze reports to assist in making key sales decisions</p><p>- Manage in-store devices in order to capitalize on a wider range of products</p><p>- Following a weekly brief, ensure that this is applied to your store and maintain high visual standards</p><p>- Attract, engage, and motivate customers to make purchases in-store by using the latest visual techniques</p><p>- Making sure that all new products and advertised products are visible and in the correct locations</p><p>- Ensure mannequins, displays, and windows are updated in accordance with Visual Merchandising guidelines</p><p>- Develop existing team members and encourage progression within the company</p><p>- Hold regular training meetings within the store, making sure the team around you is able to maintain the high standards required</p><p>- Keep track of internal progression</p><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><p>- Minimum 2 - 3 years of team management experience in relevant industry</p><p>- Passion for fashion, styling, and customer service</p><p>- Strong communication and interpersonal skills</p><p>- Ability to work in a fast-paced retail environment</p><p>- Flexibility to work shifts, weekends, and public holidays</p><p><strong>Compensation:</strong></p><p>- Working locations: ION / VIVO</p><p>- Working hours: 5 days per week / 9-hrs shift per day (early, middle, late)</p><p>- Working time varies by store</p><p>- Outpatient coverage: SGD 400</p><p>- Health screening, dental & optical: SGD 300</p><p>- Insurance coverage: Group Term Life, Hospitalization & Surgical</p><p>- Birthday voucher, Marriage gift card, Newborn gift</p><p>- 14 days annual leave<a href=\"https://www.jointhire.com.sg/job/3558?utm_source=followup\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></p>",
